rt and ATMI was all around pleased."},{"modifiedDate":"2021-06-16T16:23:09.423","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"vessel required bunkers at Port Arthur outbound - port is interim but tugs for shift to anchorage for our account"}],"offhireList":[],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}